properties.name: cabd.maxresults
properties.description: The maximum number of results returned for any barrier search

properties.name: cabd.vectorcachesize
properties.description: The maximum size of the vector tile cache before items are evicted

properties.name: cabd.cachefree
properties.description: The amount of free space to aim for when evicting items from the cache

properties.name: cabd.cachecleanupdelay
properties.description: The amount of time in seconds between vector tile cache clearing
